node.text: When Hobbs Kessler passes you, the race is as good as done. With his speed and stamina, @Hobbs_Kessler posted official times like 3:34.36 in the 1500m (No. 1 U.S. & All-Time Rank), 8:39.04 in the 2-mile (No. 1 U.S. Rank), and 1:49.67 in the 800m (No. 3 U.S. Rank). Congrats to Michigan’s finest, Hobbs Kessler, on winning the 2020-21 National Boys Track & Field #GatoradePOY 🏆

node.text: Dylan Lesko is a special talent on and off the mound including fielding a 4.0 GPA. With that said, it was a no brainer why he was the first HS Junior ever chosen to win the 2020-21 National Baseball #GatoradePOY. Watch @lindor12bc surprise @dylanlesko26 with the award and hear from his coach on just the type of player and person Dylan really is
